# Success Metrics

## Engagement Metrics

| Metric | Purpose |
|----------|----------|
| Session Duration | Measures visitor interest |
| Tour Completion Rate | Measures engagement depth |
| Repeat Visits | Measures customer intent |
| Hotspot Clicks | Measures interaction |

---

## Conversion Metrics

| Metric | Purpose |
|----------|----------|
| Leads Generated | Measures demand |
| Booking Requests | Measures purchase intent |
| Contact Form Submissions | Measures conversion |
| Qualified Leads | Measures lead quality |

---

## Financial Metrics

| Metric | Formula |
|----------|----------|
| Cost of Tour | Project Cost |
| Revenue Generated | Sales Attributed |
| ROI | ((Revenue - Cost) / Cost) × 100 |

---

# Example Scenario

## Hotel Property

Virtual Tour Cost:

KES 50,000

Monthly Additional Bookings:

10

Average Booking Value:

KES 12,000

Monthly Revenue Generated:

KES 120,000

---

## ROI Calculation

Revenue Generated:

KES 120,000

Cost:

KES 50,000

ROI:

((120,000 - 50,000) / 50,000) × 100

ROI = 140%

